04/12/2009
SKOPJE, Macedonia -- Police seized 45kg of marijuana, four guns, bullets and a hand grenade in two separate actions Thursday (December 3rd).
Kumanovo police spokesperson Valentina Nikolovska says the marijuana was seized in the village of Goshnice, in the Macedonia-Kosovo border zone, while the guns and munitions were seized in the city of Kumanovo.
(Koha Ditore, Express - 04/12/09)
